Metadata.Title: Kill Order: The Rats
Metadata.Description: An Unfortunete series of events lead us to a unique opportunity. Without being able to recover any data on our go betweens contacts due to alma drowning herself. We had no other option than to pursue leads through Orison. We managed to find a training camp through geo detection of an online post. It appears he was busy after his time with ICU. Orison was one of two trainers to a rogue group we now know is responsible for several of our agents deaths. Infiltrate and gather data via Maya Parvati.
